channel.title: Youtube messed up?
channel.description: I've tried to upload a video multiple times, and I get a failed upload every time. [IMG]http://i51.tinypic.com/1566d7p.png[/img] At the top, it says "third times the charm?" because that's the third time I tried uploading the video. I removed the log for the first two. Then, I rerendered the video, and saved it as "screwtube.wmv". Still get the same error. Is youtube having difficulties, or is something wrong with my computer? It will get about 50% done, and just abort.
